scenes.description: Amelia Watson investigates Takanashi Kiara's 'crimes' at the height chart mugshot wall.
Gawr Gura is investigated and measured against Amelia and then Mori Calliope.
Mori Calliope takes her turn at the mugshot wall while Amelia inspects her.
Ninomae Ina'nis is accused of puns and cookie withholding, leading to a tentacle outburst.
